"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:19:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d178d8b0b05d0dd5e72d81d5ba666101f4bd0e5","tid":532427,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:43:06.000Z","msg":"狗到"},{"pid":"4d6026b9cd4895a8d5686a3986130087d2f52687","tid":532427,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff6f098acda228f4491c13840a9aecd68aab4a96","tid":532427,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:02:02.000Z","msg":"新建停車場若設電動車充電裝置，可獲寬免停車場的總樓面面積<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用唔到都可以寬免 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:47:21.000Z","msg":"冇話電動車充電裝置要用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04749e83f477005caf55d90a6569c45893cbbd53","tid":532427,"uid":126046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:48:05.000Z","msg":"啲支那文化落到黎啦 屌"}]}